# Cloudflare Pages _redirects
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

# 1. /sitemap.xml → sitemap-index.xml (Google probes default location)
/sitemap.xml /sitemap-index.xml 301

# 2. Trailing slash normalisation handled by Astro `trailingSlash: 'always'`
# 3. Double-slash normalisation — Cloudflare auto-normalises consecutive
#    slashes in URL paths at the edge before this file runs.

# 4. Legacy / common typo redirects
/sitemap/ /sitemap-index.xml 301
/sitemap /sitemap-index.xml 301
/calculator/ /calculators/ 301
/all/ /calculators/ 301
/all-calculators/ /calculators/ 301
